WEBVTT

00:01.102 --> 00:02.703
male announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:02.736 --> 00:06.307
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:06.340 --> 00:08.609
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:08.642 --> 00:10.411
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:10.444 --> 00:12.046
ARE MEMBERS OF
AN ELITE SQUAD

00:12.080 --> 00:14.182
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:14.215 --> 00:16.350
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:20.654 --> 00:24.658
- [breathing heavily]

00:37.805 --> 00:41.309
- YOU GET YOUR CONFESSION?

00:41.342 --> 00:43.844
- NINE HOURS.
GUY HELD OUT FOR NINE HOURS.

00:43.877 --> 00:46.547
- WELL, THE DESK SERGEANT
ASKED ME TO BRING THIS UP.

00:46.580 --> 00:48.282
YOU WANT A CUP OF COFFEE?

00:48.316 --> 00:50.551
- YEAH, AND TWO EGGS
OVER EASY,

00:50.584 --> 00:52.386
SOME HASHBROWNS,
AND TOAST.

00:52.420 --> 00:55.156
COFFEE'S FINE.

01:07.235 --> 01:10.271
- MATLOCK,
JUDGMENT DAY.

01:13.241 --> 01:15.176
[applause]

01:15.209 --> 01:19.780
DON'T GET YOUR HOPES UP,
SON.

01:19.813 --> 01:22.283
- WELCOME BACK, MR. PENA.

01:22.316 --> 01:23.651
I UNDERSTAND YOU'RE
REPRESENTING YOURSELF.

01:23.684 --> 01:24.652
- YES, YOUR HONOR.

01:24.685 --> 01:26.554
- MOTION TO VACATE CONVICTION

01:26.587 --> 01:28.589
BASED ON NEW EVIDENCE.

01:28.622 --> 01:30.124
WHAT NEW EVIDENCE?

01:30.158 --> 01:32.293
- THE EVIDENCE
WOULD BE PENDING A RETESTING

01:32.326 --> 01:33.461
OF THE DNA
AT THE CRIME SCENE.

01:33.494 --> 01:34.728
- THERE WAS NO DNA
FOUND AT THE SCENE.

01:34.762 --> 01:36.897
- NONE FOUND
BASED ON THE TECHNOLOGY

01:36.930 --> 01:38.599
AT THE TIME,
BUT WITH NEW TECHNIQUES,

01:38.632 --> 01:41.302
DNA CAN BE RECOVERED
FROM MUCH SMALLER AMOUNTS

01:41.335 --> 01:42.736
OF TRACE EVIDENCE.

01:42.770 --> 01:45.173
- YOU'RE ASKING THE COURT
TO OVERTURN YOUR CONVICTION

01:45.206 --> 01:46.174
BASED ON EVIDENCE
YOU DON'T HAVE.

01:46.207 --> 01:48.342
- THE STATE HAS THE MEANS
AT THEIR DISPOSAL

01:48.376 --> 01:49.610
TO PROVE THAT
I'M NOT THE MAN

01:49.643 --> 01:51.379
WHO COMMITTED
THIS HORRIBLE CRIME.

01:51.412 --> 01:53.347
- BY THAT YOU MEAN THE CRIME
YOU CONFESSED TO?

01:53.381 --> 01:56.850
THE RAPE AND TORTURE
OF ARIEL BASKINS.

01:56.884 --> 01:59.320
YOU TIED HER UP,
STABBED HER,

01:59.353 --> 02:01.255
AND TRIED TO BLIND HER
WITH AMMONIA.

02:01.289 --> 02:04.692
- AS I HAVE MAINTAINED
FOR EIGHT YEARS,

02:04.725 --> 02:09.530
THAT CONFESSION WAS ELICITED
UNDER EXTREME DURESS.

02:09.563 --> 02:12.400
YOUR HONOR, I RECANTED IT
AS SOON AS--

02:12.433 --> 02:13.434
- AFTER PLEADING GUILTY.

02:13.467 --> 02:16.604
AFTER THE VICTIM
I.D.'D YOU.

02:16.637 --> 02:19.440
YOU HAVE FAILED TO MEET
THE STANDARD

02:19.473 --> 02:20.674
TO OVERTURN YOUR CONVICTION.

02:20.708 --> 02:24.845
THE MOTION IS DENIED.
[gavel bangs]

02:24.878 --> 02:27.348
[indistinct chatter]

02:27.381 --> 02:30.418
- [giggling]
I'M SORRY.

02:30.451 --> 02:31.385
MMM.

02:31.419 --> 02:33.687
OH, WE'RE GOING DANCING.
YOU WANT TO COME?

02:33.721 --> 02:34.922
- I THINK I'LL PASS.

02:34.955 --> 02:36.524
- OH, COME ON.
YOU'LL MEET SOMEONE THERE.

02:36.557 --> 02:39.227
- NO, I'M FINE.
- [groans] FINE.

02:39.260 --> 02:42.263
CALL ME TOMORROW.
NOT TOO EARLY!

02:47.868 --> 02:50.604
- [screams]

02:50.638 --> 02:56.644
[sobbing]

03:16.797 --> 03:18.666
- DAVID.

03:18.699 --> 03:20.434
UH, SORRY TO SNEAK OUT
ON YOU LIKE THAT.

03:20.468 --> 03:21.935
I-I WOULD'VE WOKEN YOU,

03:21.969 --> 03:27.241
BUT THEN I PROBABLY NEVER
WOULD HAVE LEFT.

03:27.275 --> 03:30.311
- THE VICTIM
IS GINA LOGAN, 23.

03:30.344 --> 03:32.913
UNIS RESPONDED
TO HER 911 CALL,

03:32.946 --> 03:34.382
FOUND HER TIED TO THE BED.

03:34.415 --> 03:36.584
NOW SHE TOLD THEM THE ATTACKER
FORCED HER INSIDE

03:36.617 --> 03:39.019
AND WORE A SAILOR'S UNIFORM.

03:39.052 --> 03:41.722
- RIGHT, IT'S PAN AMERICAN
FLEET WEEK.

03:41.755 --> 03:42.990
ALL THOSE NAVY BOYS IN TOWN.

03:43.023 --> 03:44.558
- EMS TOOK HER OVER TO MERCY.

03:44.592 --> 03:47.428
SHE'S OUT OF ICU BUT STILL
IN SERIOUS CONDITION.

03:47.461 --> 03:49.663
THEY SAID
HE POURED AMMONIA

03:49.697 --> 03:53.367
IN HER EYES,
TRYING TO BLIND HER.

03:53.401 --> 03:54.935
NEIGHBORS DIDN'T HEAR
ANYTHING.

03:54.968 --> 03:57.438
- WAS SHE GAGGED?
- YEAH.

03:57.471 --> 03:59.407
- HOLD ON.

03:59.440 --> 04:01.642
DID HE CUT HER
BELOW THE CHEST?

04:01.675 --> 04:04.378
- YEAH, THREE SLASHES.

04:04.412 --> 04:05.679
- SON OF A BITCH.

04:05.713 --> 04:07.515
- WHAT, YOU KNOW THIS GUY?

04:07.548 --> 04:09.483
- YEAH.

04:09.517 --> 04:12.320
WE PUT HIM AWAY FOR LIFE
EIGHT YEARS AGO.

04:15.489 --> 04:18.492
BUT THIS IS HIM.

04:20.361 --> 04:23.331
[dramatic music]

04:23.364 --> 04:31.372
*

05:06.674 --> 05:07.941
- ARE YOU SURE?
OMAR PENA?

05:07.975 --> 05:09.543
- I SPOKE TO THE WARDEN MYSELF.

05:09.577 --> 05:11.379
PENA WAS IN HIS CELL
AT GREEN HAVEN

05:11.412 --> 05:12.446
AS OF TEN MINUTES AGO.

05:12.480 --> 05:14.382
- THIS IS HIS EXACT M.O.

05:14.415 --> 05:16.784
THE NAVY UNIFORM,
FLEET WEEK,

05:16.817 --> 05:18.619
THE TORTURE,
THE AMMONIA.

05:18.652 --> 05:20.888
IF YOU TOLD ME THAT SOMEBODY
TOOK HIS PLACE IN PRISON,

05:20.921 --> 05:21.889
I WOULD BELIEVE IT.

05:21.922 --> 05:23.691
- YOU KNOW WHAT?
IT'S POSSIBLE.

05:23.724 --> 05:26.460
I MEAN, PENA HAD A HEARING
IN THE CITY A WEEK AGO

05:26.494 --> 05:27.761
TO GET HIS CONVICTION
OVERTURNED.

05:27.795 --> 05:30.130
HE LOST, BUT MAYBE
HE STAGED A FLIP.

05:30.163 --> 05:31.565
- OKAY, LET'S JUST BACK UP.

05:31.599 --> 05:32.800
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT
LAST NIGHT'S ATTACK?

05:32.833 --> 05:34.802
- YEAH.
- HOW'S THE VICTIM?

05:34.835 --> 05:36.704
- GINA LOGAN.

05:36.737 --> 05:39.740
CHEMICAL BURNS TO THE EYES
AND THROAT, SLASH WOUNDS.

05:39.773 --> 05:40.908
HE DID A NUMBER ON HER.

05:40.941 --> 05:42.843
- ANY LEADS?
- NO, NOT YET.

05:42.876 --> 05:44.678
NO WITNESSES. CSU IS STILL
CHECKING FOR PRINTS,

05:44.712 --> 05:46.046
RUNNING THE RAPE KIT.

05:46.079 --> 05:48.816
- BUT YOU THINK
YOU KNOW THIS GUY?

05:48.849 --> 05:50.451
- WE PUT OMAR PENA AWAY
IN 2004.

05:50.484 --> 05:51.785
HE CONFESSED.

05:51.819 --> 05:54.722
THE VICTIM, ARIEL BASKINS,
I.D.'D HIM.

05:54.755 --> 05:56.023
HE SPENT THE LAST EIGHT YEARS
RECANTING.

05:56.056 --> 05:57.625
- DID HE HAVE AN ACCOMPLICE?

05:57.658 --> 05:58.959
- NO, I REMEMBER THIS ONE.

05:58.992 --> 06:01.161
THE VICTIM WAS ALONE WITH HIM
FOR TEN HOURS IN HELL,

06:01.194 --> 06:03.764
GAGGED WITH HER OWN SCARF,

06:03.797 --> 06:04.798
BOUND IN ROPE.

06:04.832 --> 06:06.467
THE GUY NEVER SAID A WORD.

06:06.500 --> 06:07.568
THERE WAS NO PARTNER.

06:07.601 --> 06:09.637
- OKAY,
SO WHAT DID PENA DO?

06:09.670 --> 06:11.805
SWITCH PLACES
WITH A DOPPELGANGER

06:11.839 --> 06:13.807
WHILE HE WAS BEING TRANSFERRED
AFTER THE HEARING?

06:13.841 --> 06:16.644
- MAYBE HE GOT SOMEBODY
ON THE OUTSIDE TO MIMIC HIS M.O.

06:16.677 --> 06:19.580
- A COPYCAT. THROW SUSPICION
ON HIS CONVICTION.

06:19.613 --> 06:22.015
- EITHER WAY, YOU TWO
HEAD UP TO GREEN HAVEN,

06:22.049 --> 06:23.551
TALK TO WHOEVER'S
IN PENA'S CELL.

06:23.584 --> 06:24.585
FIN, ROLLINS,
GO TO THE HOSPITAL.

06:24.618 --> 06:28.722
SEE IF THE DOCTORS
WILL LET YOU INTERVIEW GINA.

06:31.492 --> 06:34.828
- GINA,
I'M DETECTIVE ROLLINS.

06:34.862 --> 06:36.697
CAN YOU TALK, HONEY?

06:36.730 --> 06:38.432
- [whimpering]
A LITTLE.

06:38.466 --> 06:39.633
- OKAY.

06:39.667 --> 06:42.436
JUST A FEW QUESTIONS.

06:42.470 --> 06:45.439
THAT MAN THAT ATTACKED YOU--
HAD YOU SEEN HIM BEFORE?

06:46.974 --> 06:48.442
- NO.

06:48.476 --> 06:51.512
- WAS HE WHITE?

06:51.545 --> 06:56.950
- HISPANIC.

06:56.984 --> 07:00.988
IN A WHITE NAVY UNIFORM.

07:01.021 --> 07:04.592
- DID HE HAVE AN ACCENT?

07:04.625 --> 07:06.860
- HE NEVER SPOKE.

07:06.894 --> 07:13.133
- DETECTIVE, THE DOCTOR TOLD YOU
TO COME BACK TOMORROW.

07:13.166 --> 07:15.836
- COURTNEY, WHERE WAS THIS BAR
YOU TWO WERE HANGING OUT IN?

07:15.869 --> 07:18.706
- A DIVE. I ALWAYS GO THERE
WHEN THE SHIPS ARE IN.

07:18.739 --> 07:19.840
TALKED GINA
INTO COMING WITH ME.

07:19.873 --> 07:22.910
- HEY, DID ANY HISPANIC SAILORS
TALK TO THE TWO OF YOU?

07:22.943 --> 07:26.046
- IT'S PAN AM FLEET WEEK.
IT WAS LIKE THE U.N. IN THERE.

07:26.079 --> 07:28.682
- WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
THAT YOU SAW GINA?

07:28.716 --> 07:32.019
- OUTSIDE THE BAR
AROUND MIDNIGHT.

07:32.052 --> 07:33.621
I'D HOOKED UP
WITH THIS OFFICER.

07:33.654 --> 07:35.523
WE WERE HEADED TO A CLUB.

07:35.556 --> 07:37.758
GINA FELT LIKE THE THIRD WHEEL,
SO SHE WALKED HOME.

07:37.791 --> 07:40.761
- MM.

07:40.794 --> 07:43.230
- SHE WAS DRUNK.

07:43.263 --> 07:45.232
NEVER SHOULD'VE
LEFT HER ALONE.

07:45.265 --> 07:48.802
- MY ROPE GUY FROM CSU
HAS GOT SOMETHING.

07:48.836 --> 07:51.972
- YOU GOT A ROPE GUY?
- YEAH.

07:52.005 --> 07:54.942
GUESS I'VE BEEN ON THIS JOB
TOO LONG.

07:57.578 --> 07:58.946
- THE ROPE
YOUR RAPIST USED

07:58.979 --> 08:01.749
IS A TRIPLE-BRAIDED
NYLON POLYESTER.

08:01.782 --> 08:03.817
- SORRY, BUT THAT DOESN'T
NARROW IT DOWN MUCH.

08:03.851 --> 08:05.853
- I'M MORE INTERESTED
IN THE KNOT.

08:05.886 --> 08:07.688
NOW FOR A BINDING VICTIM,

08:07.721 --> 08:08.889
WE USUALLY FIND
A SIMPLE OVERHAND KNOT.

08:08.922 --> 08:11.659
THIS GUY USED A CLOVE HITCH
ON THE WRIST

08:11.692 --> 08:13.894
AND BOWLINE TO TIE
TO THE BED.

08:13.927 --> 08:15.696
- OKAY, WELL,
HE WORE A NAVY UNIFORM.

08:15.729 --> 08:16.964
THESE ARE SAILOR'S KNOTS,
RIGHT?

08:16.997 --> 08:18.632
- WELL, IT'S DEFINITELY
SOMETHING THEY TEACH

08:18.666 --> 08:19.900
IN NAVY TRAINING.

08:19.933 --> 08:22.970
THERE'S ONE MORE THING.

08:23.003 --> 08:25.739
YOU SEE HOW I WRAP
THE WORKING END AROUND

08:25.773 --> 08:28.842
AND FINISH ON THE INSIDE?

08:28.876 --> 08:33.113
NOW WHOEVER TIED THESE
FINISHED ON THE OUTSIDE.

08:33.146 --> 08:37.985
IT MEANS HE'S LEFT-HANDED.

08:38.018 --> 08:40.554
- I'M IN PRISON
TWO HOURS AWAY,

08:40.588 --> 08:43.223
AND YOU THINK I SOMEHOW
RAPED SOMEONE AGAIN?

08:43.256 --> 08:46.994
YOU HER NEW PARTNER?

08:47.027 --> 08:48.962
SHE'S HAD A HARD-ON FOR ME
FOR EIGHT YEARS.

08:48.996 --> 08:50.798
- WATCH IT, OMAR.
- WHAT, ME?

08:50.831 --> 08:52.700
SHE PUT ME AWAY FOR A CRIME
THAT I DIDN'T COMMIT.

08:52.733 --> 08:54.001
- A CRIME
THAT YOU CONFESSED TO.

08:54.034 --> 08:56.103
- I WAS IN THERE ALL NIGHT,
OKAY?

08:56.136 --> 08:58.138
NO FOOD, NO WATER.

08:58.171 --> 08:59.973
I WANTED TO GET OUT
OF THERE.

09:00.007 --> 09:01.008
- THE VICTIM I.D.'D YOU.

09:01.041 --> 09:04.578
YOU HAD HER CREDIT CARDS
WHEN WE ARRESTED YOU.

09:04.612 --> 09:06.880
- I TOLD YOU THAT I FOUND THEM
IN A DUMPSTER.

09:06.914 --> 09:09.016
- WELL, YOU DIDN'T HAVE
AN ALIBI, DID YOU?

09:09.049 --> 09:11.952
- I PARTIED ALL NIGHT.
I SMOKED A COUPLE OF JOINTS.

09:11.985 --> 09:12.986
I ALREADY HAD TWO PRIORS.

09:13.020 --> 09:15.288
I COULDN'T TELL YOU THAT.
- THAT MAKES SENSE.

09:15.322 --> 09:17.791
YOU'RE SORRY YOU CONFESSED.

09:17.825 --> 09:18.959
SO WHAT'D YOU DO?

09:18.992 --> 09:22.229
GET ONE OF YOUR BOYS
ON THE OUTSIDE

09:22.262 --> 09:24.031
TO COPYCAT YOUR CRIME,
PROVE IT WASN'T YOU?

09:24.064 --> 09:26.066
- NO, MAN.
NO.

09:26.099 --> 09:29.036
- WHO WAS IT, OMAR?

09:29.069 --> 09:31.772
ONE OF YOUR PRISON CELLMATES?

09:31.805 --> 09:34.007
JUST GIVE US HIS NAME.
WE WON'T EVEN CHARGE YOU.

09:34.041 --> 09:35.709
- CHARGE ME?

09:35.743 --> 09:37.611
I'M IN JAIL FOR 300 YEARS.

09:37.645 --> 09:39.980
- AND YOU EARNED
EVERY SINGLE ONE OF THEM.

09:40.013 --> 09:42.750
NOW YOU PUT
ANOTHER WOMAN

09:42.783 --> 09:44.985
THROUGH THIS HORROR
TO MAINTAIN YOUR LIES?

09:45.018 --> 09:48.656
- I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

09:48.689 --> 09:51.058
- NO? A WEEK AFTER YOUR FINAL
HEARING WAS DENIED,

09:51.091 --> 09:52.726
THE EXACT SAME DETAILS?

09:52.760 --> 09:54.862
- YEAH, AND WHAT DOES THAT
TELL YOU, HUH?

09:54.895 --> 09:56.296
IT ISN'T ME THIS TIME.

09:56.329 --> 09:58.398
IT WASN'T ME THEN.

09:58.431 --> 10:00.133
YOU GOT SOME SICK PRICK
STILL OUT THERE,

10:00.167 --> 10:01.902
AND INSTEAD OF
LOOKING FOR HIM,

10:01.935 --> 10:03.937
YOU'RE WASTING
YOUR TIME ON ME.

10:03.971 --> 10:06.273
- YOU'RE NOT
A WASTE OF TIME.

10:06.306 --> 10:09.009
YOU'RE A WASTE
OF A LIFE.

10:09.042 --> 10:13.046
YOU CONFESSED BECAUSE YOU KNEW
WHAT YOU HAD DONE.

10:13.080 --> 10:15.816
- ALL RIGHT, LIV,
WE'RE DONE HERE.

10:15.849 --> 10:19.219
COME ON.

10:19.252 --> 10:20.921
- [whistles]
DETECTIVE AMARO.

10:20.954 --> 10:23.023
ABOUT THAT CONFESSION,

10:23.056 --> 10:25.926
I TOOK IT BACK
THE FIRST CHANCE I GOT.

10:25.959 --> 10:26.927
SHE TELL YOU THAT?

10:26.960 --> 10:29.062
- YEAH? WHEN WAS THAT?

10:29.096 --> 10:32.365
BEFORE OR AFTER
YOU GOT SENTENCED?

10:32.399 --> 10:34.702
HAPPENS ALL THE TIME, OMAR.

10:34.735 --> 10:37.037
- YEAH, SHE DIDN'T CARE.

10:37.070 --> 10:40.340
NOBODY DID!
RIGHT?

10:40.373 --> 10:43.977
ONCE YOU CONFESS,
EVERYBODY STOPS LISTENING!

10:46.013 --> 10:48.949
- PENA'S BEEN BURIED IN LAW
BOOKS EVER SINCE HE GOT HERE.

10:48.982 --> 10:50.183
SENDING LETTERS.

10:50.217 --> 10:52.152
GUYS IN HIS CELL BLOCK
CALL HIM MATLOCK.

10:52.185 --> 10:53.754
- WE'LL NEED A LIST
OF EVERYONE

10:53.787 --> 10:55.756
HE WAS IN CONTACT WITH
ON THE OUTSIDE.

10:55.789 --> 10:57.925
- SHORT LIST.
HE DOESN'T GET ANY VISITORS.

10:57.958 --> 10:58.959
- THERE'S NO FAMILY?

10:58.992 --> 11:02.095
- HIS MOTHER DIED A YEAR
AFTER HE GOT SENT AWAY.

11:02.129 --> 11:03.430
SHE'S THE ONLY ONE
THAT CAME.

11:03.463 --> 11:05.165
- THAT WHEN HE STARTED
HIS LETTER-WRITING CAMPAIGN?

11:05.198 --> 11:07.034
- MORE LIKE
HE BECAME OBSESSED.

11:07.067 --> 11:11.071
20 LETTERS A DAY,
7 DAYS A WEEK.

11:11.104 --> 11:13.106
- OKAY.
THANK YOU.

11:13.140 --> 11:16.009
- ALL RIGHT, LOOK, IF PENA
HAS SOMEONE ON THE OUTSIDE,

11:16.043 --> 11:17.745
HE DIDN'T WRITE TO THEM.

11:17.778 --> 11:20.113
ALL THESE LETTERS
ARE TO LAWYERS, MINISTERS,

11:20.147 --> 11:22.282
JOURNALISTS, CONGRESSMEN,
THE PRESIDENT.

11:22.315 --> 11:24.117
- OKAY, DID ANYONE
WRITE HIM BACK?

11:24.151 --> 11:28.121
- YEAH, YOUR PAL ELLIS
ABOUT A MONTH AGO.

11:28.155 --> 11:30.023
TOLD PENA
HE'D LOOK INTO IT.

11:30.057 --> 11:31.291
- LOOK, YOU SHOULD SEE
ELLIS' OFFICE.

11:31.324 --> 11:33.226
HE GETS 100 LETTERS
LIKE THIS A MONTH.

11:33.260 --> 11:34.962
- I'LL PASS.

11:34.995 --> 11:36.897
- HEY.
ANY LUCK AT THE BAR?

11:36.930 --> 11:38.799
- BRAS AND THONGS
ON THE CEILING,

11:38.832 --> 11:40.133
NO SECURITY CAMERAS.

11:40.167 --> 11:41.802
NOBODY EVEN REMEMBERS
SEEING GINA.

11:41.835 --> 11:43.837
- YEAH, WELL, FLEET WEEK
DOESN'T PRODUCE

11:43.871 --> 11:46.039
THE MOST RELIABLE WITNESSES.
- MM.

11:46.073 --> 11:49.076
- AS OF NOW, ALL WE'VE GOT ON
THE SATURDAY NIGHT ATTACKER

11:49.109 --> 11:50.811
IS HE WAS LEFT-HANDED,
LATINO,

11:50.844 --> 11:52.746
AND WAS WEARING A WHITE
SAILOR'S UNIFORM.

11:52.780 --> 11:54.815
- A LEFTY?
- YEAH, FROM THE KNOTS.

11:54.848 --> 11:57.084
CSU IS CHECKING THE ROPE
FROM EIGHT YEARS AGO

11:57.117 --> 11:58.185
TO SEE IF THERE'S A MATCH.

11:58.218 --> 11:59.119
- I GOT A LIST
OF INMATES RELEASED

11:59.152 --> 12:02.055
FROM GREEN HAVEN
SINCE PENA'S BEEN THERE.

12:02.089 --> 12:04.758
CROSS-CHECKED WITH
A NAVY DATABASE, GOT ONE HIT.

12:04.792 --> 12:06.259
MIKE MARTINEZ.

12:06.293 --> 12:09.062
HE'S EX-NAVY,
DISHONORABLE DISCHARGE.

12:09.096 --> 12:09.930
- HOW DID HE WIND UP
IN GREEN HAVEN?

12:09.963 --> 12:12.132
- HE WAS CHARGED
WITH ATTEMPTED RAPE,

12:12.165 --> 12:14.835
BUT HE PLED DOWN TO A FIVE-YEAR
STRETCH FOR ASSAULT.

12:14.868 --> 12:17.070
HE MADE PAROLE
THREE MONTHS AGO.

12:17.104 --> 12:19.072
GET THIS.
THE LAWYER THAT PREPPED HIM--

12:19.106 --> 12:22.375
OMAR PENA.

12:24.878 --> 12:28.148
- OMAR PENA
GOT MARTINEZ OUT.

12:30.017 --> 12:33.120
DO YOU HAVE HIS PAROLE OFFICER?
- YEAH.

12:33.153 --> 12:35.856
- LET'S SEE IF MARTINEZ
PAID BACK THE FAVOR.

12:38.191 --> 12:39.192
[knocking at door]

12:39.226 --> 12:41.161
- GLADYS MARTINEZ.

12:41.194 --> 12:44.197
OPEN UP.
IT'S THE POLICE.

12:44.231 --> 12:45.565
- GLADYS ISN'T HERE.

12:45.598 --> 12:49.002
- UH, WE'RE LOOKING
FOR HER SON MIKE.

