AND SO HE SPLASHED ME
IN THE FACE.

23:41.821 --> 23:44.657
- RIGHT, SO YOU RECOGNIZE HIM
FROM THE BAR,

23:44.691 --> 23:45.658
NOT FROM THE ATTACK?

23:45.692 --> 23:47.794
- IT WAS HIM.

23:47.827 --> 23:49.228
I DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU'RE ASKING ME ALL OF THIS.

23:49.261 --> 23:51.931
YOU TOLD ME YOURSELF
HE KNEW ALL THOSE DETAILS.

23:51.964 --> 23:56.636
HE KNEW ABOUT THE SCARF
THAT HE USED TO GAG ME WITH.

23:56.669 --> 23:57.970
I HAVEN'T WORN RED SINCE.

23:58.004 --> 24:01.974
- WHAT DID YOU SAY?

24:02.008 --> 24:05.478
YOU SAID, "RED"?

24:05.512 --> 24:07.847
ARE YOU SURE THAT
THE SCARF WAS RED?

24:07.880 --> 24:11.984
- YES, IT WAS A BIRTHDAY PRESENT
FROM MY MOTHER.

24:12.018 --> 24:15.622
SAID IT WAS SUPPOSED
TO BRING ME LUCK.

24:15.655 --> 24:18.057
TELL ME
HE'S NOT GETTING OUT.

24:20.292 --> 24:23.095
- HEY, LIV,
SLOW DOWN.

24:23.129 --> 24:24.864
WHAT'S GOING ON?

24:24.897 --> 24:28.968
- ONE OF THE DETAILS
THAT ONLY THE RAPIST WOULD KNOW.

24:32.304 --> 24:34.140
THERE'S THE PAPERWORK.

24:34.173 --> 24:35.207
WHEN OMAR CONFESSED,

24:35.241 --> 24:39.078
HE SAID THAT HE USED
A GREEN SCARF TO GAG ARIEL.

24:39.111 --> 24:40.647
- YOU SURE?

24:40.680 --> 24:42.081
- I'VE GONE OVER MY NOTES
ON THIS CASE

24:42.114 --> 24:44.016
EVERY SINGLE NIGHT
SINCE GINA WAS RAPED.

24:44.050 --> 24:45.518
IT WAS THE ONE DETAIL
THAT CONVINCED US

24:45.552 --> 24:46.519
THAT OMAR WAS GUILTY.

24:46.553 --> 24:49.055
- AND JUST NOW ARIEL SAID
THE SCARF WAS RED.

24:49.088 --> 24:51.057
- DID YOU FIND IT
ON THE WORKSHEET?

24:51.090 --> 24:52.058
- YEAH, HERE WE GO.

24:52.091 --> 24:54.193
THE OFFICER
WHO VOUCHERED IT

24:54.226 --> 24:57.229
LISTED IT AS GREEN.

25:02.769 --> 25:04.804
- DOES THAT LOOK GREEN
TO YOU?

25:11.143 --> 25:15.214
- AND YOU WEREN'T
AT THE CRIME SCENE?

25:15.247 --> 25:19.151
- I WAS AT THE HOSPITAL
WITH ARIEL.

25:19.185 --> 25:23.055
- SO YOU QUESTIONED PENA
OFF AN EVIDENCE LOG

25:23.089 --> 25:24.924
THAT YOU DIDN'T KNOW
WAS WRONG.

25:24.957 --> 25:30.096
- AT SOME POINT, I MUST HAVE
MENTIONED THE GREEN SCARF.

25:30.129 --> 25:34.834
AND THEN WHEN HE WAS TIRED
AND EXHAUSTED

25:34.867 --> 25:38.004
AND CONFUSED, HE MUST HAVE
REPEATED IT BACK TO ME.

25:38.037 --> 25:40.072
- PUT HIMSELF AWAY
FOR 300 YEARS.

25:40.106 --> 25:42.341
- HE RECANTED.

25:42.374 --> 25:48.681
HE KEPT TELLING ME
THAT HE WAS INNOCENT.

25:48.715 --> 25:51.350
[sighs]

25:51.383 --> 25:54.854
[breathing heavily]

25:58.257 --> 26:00.192
- THE OFFICER WAS COLOR-BLIND?
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

26:00.226 --> 26:01.694
HOW DID HE GET
ON THE FORCE?

26:01.728 --> 26:03.863
- HE WAS FINE WHEN HE CAME OUT
OF THE ACADEMY,

26:03.896 --> 26:07.199
BUT BY 2004,
HE HAD EARLY STAGE M.S.

26:07.233 --> 26:10.336
AND ONE OF THE SYMPTOMS--
- COLOR BLINDNESS.

26:10.369 --> 26:13.339
[chuckles] SO HE LOGS IN
A RED SCARF AS GREEN?

26:13.372 --> 26:16.976
ANYTHING THAT CAN GO WRONG--

26:17.009 --> 26:20.012
- I MUST HAVE MENTIONED
THAT DETAIL TO HIM,

26:20.046 --> 26:22.749
AND THEN HOURS LATER,
HE REPEATED IT BACK TO ME.

26:22.782 --> 26:25.752
- IT COULD'VE BEEN A DETECTIVE
WHO INTERROGATED PENA EARLIER.

26:25.785 --> 26:28.254
- DOESN'T MATTER.
THE CONFESSION'S NO GOOD.

26:28.287 --> 26:31.724
- I TAKE FULL RESPONSIBILITY.

26:31.758 --> 26:33.159
- WE'RE NOT POINTING
FINGERS HERE.

26:33.192 --> 26:34.994
IF PENA'S CONFESSION
WAS COMPROMISED,

26:35.027 --> 26:37.764
AND HE'S PETITIONING
FOR A DNA TEST, HE DESERVES ONE.

26:37.797 --> 26:40.967
- A COUPLE OF DAYS AGO,
YOUR DETECTIVE ASSURED ME

26:41.000 --> 26:42.334
THAT I HAD
A GOOD CONFESSION.

26:42.368 --> 26:43.803
I TOOK HER WORD
ON THAT.

26:43.836 --> 26:45.071
WE'RE ALL OUT
ON A LIMB HERE.

26:45.104 --> 26:46.238
- PEOPLE MAKE MISTAKES.

26:46.272 --> 26:47.907
DETECTIVE BENSON
HAS STEPPED FORWARD.

26:47.940 --> 26:49.175
- I AM NOT ARGUING CHARACTER.

26:49.208 --> 26:52.078
THIS IS ABOUT PERCEPTION.

26:54.681 --> 26:56.783
ELLIS IS GONNA TURN THIS
INTO AN INDICTMENT

26:56.816 --> 27:00.720
OF BOTH OF OUR OFFICES.

27:00.753 --> 27:04.123
- OKAY, LET ME TALK
TO ELLIS AND TELL HIM

27:04.156 --> 27:06.859
THAT THIS WAS ENTIRELY
MY MISTAKE.

27:06.893 --> 27:08.260
- DON'T BARE YOUR NECK
TO A WOLF.

27:08.294 --> 27:09.796
JUST TELL HIM THAT
THE D.A.'S OFFICE

27:09.829 --> 27:12.832
WILL MOVE TO GET
THE DNA TEST APPROVED.

27:24.310 --> 27:26.913
- WE FOUND MATCHING
TOUCH DNA ON THE ROPES

27:26.946 --> 27:28.681
AT BOTH CRIME SCENES.

27:28.715 --> 27:30.416
THAT MEANS IT WASN'T YOU,
OMAR.

27:30.449 --> 27:33.352
THEY'RE REOPENING THE CASE.

27:33.385 --> 27:37.156
AT THE VERY LEAST,
IF IT HAS TO GO TO RETRIAL,

27:37.189 --> 27:39.959
THERE WILL BE
REASONABLE DOUBT.

27:39.992 --> 27:42.128
- OMAR.

27:42.161 --> 27:43.830
- WHAT?

27:43.863 --> 27:48.701
A REINVESTIGATION?
A RETRIAL?

27:48.735 --> 27:50.136
YOU WANT A GOLD MEDAL NOW?

27:50.169 --> 27:51.904
HUH?
YOU'RE TELLING ME SOMETHING

27:51.938 --> 27:55.141
THAT I TOLD YOU
EIGHT YEARS AGO.

27:55.174 --> 27:56.475
- TAKE IT EASY, OMAR.

27:56.508 --> 27:58.144
- I'M INNOCENT.
I DON'T WANT A RETRIAL.

27:58.177 --> 27:59.912
I WANT THEM
TO VACATE MY CONVICTION.

27:59.946 --> 28:02.014
- THERE IS LIGHT
AT THE END OF THIS TUNNEL.

28:02.048 --> 28:09.488
- I'LL BELIEVE THAT
WHEN I'M OUT.

28:09.521 --> 28:13.860
- THE CONFESSION
WAS ALL MY FAULT.

28:13.893 --> 28:16.328
I WORKED HIM HARD.

28:16.362 --> 28:19.298
I TOLD HIM THAT WE HAD
ALL KINDS OF EVIDENCE.

28:19.331 --> 28:23.369
I TOLD HIM THAT HE WAS
GOING AWAY NO MATTER WHAT.

28:23.402 --> 28:24.971
I BROKE HIM.

28:25.004 --> 28:26.739
- YOU WERE DOING YOUR JOB.

28:26.773 --> 28:31.744
- I FORCED A FALSE CONFESSION.

28:31.778 --> 28:33.980
ARE THERE OTHERS?

28:34.013 --> 28:37.817
I LOOK IN THE MIRROR,
I DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE.

28:37.850 --> 28:39.786
- OLIVIA.

28:39.819 --> 28:42.054
- I'VE SEEN GOOD OLD BOY
DETECTIVES PULL THIS.

28:42.088 --> 28:44.957
AND I TOOK PRIDE IN KNOWING
THAT I WASN'T ONE OF THEM.

28:44.991 --> 28:49.161
- BECAUSE YOU'RE NOT.

28:49.195 --> 28:51.430
YOU STEPPED FORWARD.

29:05.411 --> 29:07.479
- HOW DID IT GO
AT GREEN HAVEN YESTERDAY?

29:07.513 --> 29:09.782
- HOW DO YOU THINK?

29:09.816 --> 29:11.851
- YOU KNOW, MUNCH AND I
HAD PENA FIRST.

29:11.884 --> 29:14.020
IT COULD'VE BEEN ONE OF US
WHO SLIPPED UP ON THAT SCARF.

29:14.053 --> 29:16.555
- DOESN'T MATTER.

29:16.588 --> 29:19.058
SO WHERE ARE WE ON CATCHING
THE REAL RAPIST?

29:19.091 --> 29:21.894
- NOWHERE BUT SOMEWHERE.

29:21.928 --> 29:22.795
IT TURNS OUT THAT
THERE ARE MORE

29:22.829 --> 29:24.463
THAN THE TWO RAPES
THAT HAPPENED HERE.

29:24.496 --> 29:26.999
WE GOT THREE OTHER DNA HITS

29:27.033 --> 29:28.434
FROM INTERPOL.

29:28.467 --> 29:30.102
- WHAT ARE WE LOOKING AT?

29:30.136 --> 29:33.439
- THREE SEXUAL ASSAULTS--
ONE IN BUENOS AIRES IN 2006,

29:33.472 --> 29:35.207
ANOTHER IN NAPLES, ITALY,
'08,

29:35.241 --> 29:36.976
AND THEN ROTA, SPAIN,
2009.

29:37.009 --> 29:39.311
- SO OUR SERIAL RAPIST
STARTS HERE

29:39.345 --> 29:42.248
IN 2004 WITH ARIEL,
THEN MOVES ON TO OTHER PORTS.

29:42.281 --> 29:45.584
- UNTIL HE COMES BACK,
RAPES GINA LOGAN.

29:45.617 --> 29:46.886
SAME M.O.?
- YEP.

29:46.919 --> 29:48.821
UNIFORM, AMMONIA,

29:48.855 --> 29:50.923
ALL COMMITTED BY A SINGLE
UNKNOWN SUSPECT.

29:50.957 --> 29:52.859
- SO THESE ARE ALL
PORT CITIES,

29:52.892 --> 29:55.594
SO, YOU KNOW, I CHECKED
THE SPECIFIC DATES.

29:55.627 --> 29:57.897
THEY ALL MATCH UP WITH
INTERNATIONAL FLEET WEEK EVENTS.

29:57.930 --> 30:00.199
- WE KNOW THE RAPIST
ISN'T U.S. NAVY.

30:00.232 --> 30:02.201
THEY'D HAVE HIS DNA
ON FILE.

30:02.234 --> 30:05.137
- SO THESE NAVAL UNIFORMS--

30:05.171 --> 30:09.008
HOW DIFFERENT ARE THEY
FROM ONE COUNTRY TO THE NEXT?

30:09.041 --> 30:11.043
- MY CLIENT HAS BEEN WRONGFULLY
IMPRISONED FOR EIGHT YEARS.

30:11.077 --> 30:12.845
HOW MUCH LONGER
DOES HE HAVE TO WAIT?

30:12.879 --> 30:15.447
- CAN'T LET PENA OUT UNTIL
WE COMPLETE OUR INVESTIGATION.

30:15.481 --> 30:17.349
THE DNA RESULTS ALONE
AREN'T EXCULPATORY.

30:17.383 --> 30:18.985
- PAIRED WITH
A FALSE CONFESSION,

30:19.018 --> 30:21.153
THE HELL THEY AREN'T.
- HANG ON A MINUTE.

30:21.187 --> 30:23.956
THERE'S PLENTY OF OTHER EVIDENCE
BESIDES PENA'S CONFESSION.

30:23.990 --> 30:24.991
VICTIM PICKED HIM
OUT OF A LINEUP.

30:25.024 --> 30:28.327
SIX WITNESSES I.D.'D HIM
IN A BAR HARASSING HER.

30:28.360 --> 30:30.462
HE GETS ARRESTED WITH
THE VICTIM'S CREDIT CARDS.

30:30.496 --> 30:33.632
IT'S, UH, NOT A SLAM DUNK
FOR A DISMISSAL.

30:33.665 --> 30:36.035
- CIRCUMSTANTIAL.
BAD I.D.s.

30:36.068 --> 30:38.137
- THERE'S NO MALICE HERE.

30:38.170 --> 30:41.941
NOT FROM THE D.A.'S OFFICE,
NOT FROM NYPD.

30:41.974 --> 30:43.375
DETECTIVE BENSON
IS KILLING HERSELF

30:43.409 --> 30:44.443
TRYING TO MAKE
THIS THING RIGHT.

30:44.476 --> 30:47.046
YOU SAW HER WITH PENA.
- YES, I KNOW.

30:47.079 --> 30:50.482
- SHE'S TAKING THIS
PERSONALLY.

30:50.516 --> 30:53.352
SHE'S NOT ONE OF THOSE
GOOD OL' BOY DETECTIVES.

30:53.385 --> 30:54.353
THIS IS A POINT

30:54.386 --> 30:57.389
OF PRIDE WITH HER.

30:59.525 --> 31:02.094
- MAY I ASK WHEN
DETECTIVE BENSON

31:02.128 --> 31:03.662
TOLD YOU ABOUT
OUR VISIT TO PENA?

31:03.695 --> 31:05.631
- EXCUSE ME?

31:05.664 --> 31:09.401
- YESTERDAY AFTERNOON?

31:09.435 --> 31:13.539
I WAS WITH HER ON THE TRAIN,
SO IT MUST HAVE BEEN...

31:13.572 --> 31:18.410
LAST NIGHT.

31:18.444 --> 31:20.012
- WHAT ARE YOU ASKING ME?

31:20.046 --> 31:22.081
- I'M CURIOUS.

31:22.114 --> 31:25.918
WHAT EXACTLY IS THE NATURE
OF YOUR RELATIONSHIP?

31:30.089 --> 31:31.357
- I THINK WE'RE DONE HERE.

31:31.390 --> 31:34.160
- DOES THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY
KNOW?

31:36.695 --> 31:39.331
I'VE GOT AN INNOCENT MAN
IN PRISON,

31:39.365 --> 31:42.168
AND APPEARANCES SUGGEST
THAT THE DETECTIVE

31:42.201 --> 31:43.169
WHO COERCED
THE CONFESSION

31:43.202 --> 31:46.172
IS INVOLVED
WITH THE A.D.A.

31:46.205 --> 31:49.408
WHOSE OFFICE
IS REINVESTIGATING THE CASE.

31:49.441 --> 31:53.312
- YOU KNOW US BOTH
BETTER THAN THAT.

31:53.345 --> 31:58.450
- THEN I KNOW YOU'LL BOTH
DO THE RIGHT THING HERE.

32:02.054 --> 32:05.257
[door slams]

32:05.291 --> 32:07.659
- I DON'T GET IT.

32:07.693 --> 32:09.128
ELLIS KNOWS
THAT OUR RELATIONSHIP

32:09.161 --> 32:11.163
HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THIS CASE.

32:11.197 --> 32:14.200
- HE DOES,
BUT IT GIVES HIM A GRENADE.

32:14.233 --> 32:15.634
- OKAY, SO WE HAVE
NO CHOICE.

32:15.667 --> 32:18.170
WE HAVE TO DISCLOSE.
- NO, IT'S TOO LATE.

32:18.204 --> 32:22.674
THIS COMES OUT NOW,
AFTER I VOUCHED FOR YOU,

32:22.708 --> 32:24.076
WE LOSE OUR CAREERS.

32:24.110 --> 32:26.012
- WELL, I DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHY THE D.A.

32:26.045 --> 32:27.179
WON'T RELEASE PENA.

32:27.213 --> 32:32.284
- IT DOESN'T WORK THAT WAY,
OLIVIA.

32:32.318 --> 32:36.122
OVERTURNING A GUILTY PLEA
WITH THAT MUCH EVIDENCE--

32:36.155 --> 32:37.289
IT HAS TO GO
THROUGH A PROCESS.

32:37.323 --> 32:39.391
- OKAY, SO HOW DO WE
SPEED IT UP?

32:39.425 --> 32:41.260
HOW DO WE GET OMAR
OUT OF PRISON?

32:41.293 --> 32:43.162
- IF YOU FIND
THE REAL RAPIST,

32:43.195 --> 32:46.432
TIE HIM
TO BOTH CASES,

32:46.465 --> 32:48.434
THAT EXONERATES PENA
COMPLETELY.

32:48.467 --> 32:50.102
- AND IF WE DON'T?

32:50.136 --> 32:53.739
- ELLIS HAS TO PLAY
HIS HAND.

33:00.112 --> 33:01.080
[engine starts]

33:01.113 --> 33:03.615
[seat belt alert beeps]

33:06.218 --> 33:07.419
- CAN I DROP YOU SOMEWHERE?

33:07.453 --> 33:10.522
- I'LL GET HOME
ON MY OWN.

33:23.302 --> 33:24.403
[knock on door]

33:24.436 --> 33:25.637
- BAYARD?

33:25.671 --> 33:28.640
CAN I TALK TO YOU?

33:28.674 --> 33:29.741
- SURE. COME IN.

33:29.775 --> 33:32.478
- THANK YOU.

33:32.511 --> 33:34.346
- UH, WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

33:36.182 --> 33:40.386
- DAVID HADEN AND I...

33:40.419 --> 33:42.321
IT'S NOT SOME CONSPIRACY.

33:42.354 --> 33:44.223
- NO, I DIDN'T THINK IT WAS.

33:45.491 --> 33:47.659
- WHAT YOU'RE DOING...

33:47.693 --> 33:49.295
I KNOW THAT IT'S FOR OMAR,

33:49.328 --> 33:51.097
AND I HOPE
THAT YOU KNOW ME

33:51.130 --> 33:52.298
WELL ENOUGH TO BELIEVE

33:52.331 --> 33:54.533
THAT WE WANT THE SAME THING.

33:56.702 --> 33:58.670
- I DO.

33:58.704 --> 34:00.572
BUT HOW DO I TELL OMAR

34:00.606 --> 34:02.374
I HAVE A WAY FOR HIM
TO GET OUT TODAY,

34:02.408 --> 34:04.276
BUT I CAN'T USE IT BECAUSE

34:04.310 --> 34:05.844
TWO PEOPLE MIGHT
LOSE THEIR JOBS.

34:05.877 --> 34:08.680
- I UNDERSTAND THAT.
I DO, BUT...

34:08.714 --> 34:10.616
I'M NOT HERE TO PLEAD
FOR MY CAREER

34:10.649 --> 34:11.850
OR FOR DAVID'S...

34:11.883 --> 34:14.353
- I WOULD EXPECT, IF DAVID HADEN
HAD SOMETHING TO SAY TO ME,

34:14.386 --> 34:16.522
HE'D SAY IT HIMSELF.

34:16.555 --> 34:18.424
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEANT.

34:22.494 --> 34:25.431
IS THERE ANY PART OF THIS
THAT'S...

34:25.464 --> 34:27.266
ABOUT HIM?

34:27.299 --> 34:30.469
AND YOU, AND ME?

34:32.304 --> 34:35.274
- UM, I WOULD HOPE
YOU KNOW ME WELL ENOUGH

34:35.307 --> 34:37.543
NOT TO HAVE TO ASK
THAT QUESTION.

34:37.576 --> 34:40.779
- OKAY.

34:40.812 --> 34:43.615
POINT TAKEN.

34:43.649 --> 34:49.255
- SO...WHAT CAN I
DO FOR YOU?

34:49.288 --> 34:52.824
- GIVE ME TIME.

34:52.858 --> 34:54.793
IF WE ARREST
THE REAL RAPIST,

34:54.826 --> 34:57.529
THEN OMAR GETS OUT.

34:57.563 --> 34:59.198
- HOW LONG?

34:59.231 --> 35:01.433
- A WEEK.

35:01.467 --> 35:04.403
OR I WILL GO
TO THE D.A. MYSELF

35:04.436 --> 35:07.206
AND TELL HIM EVERYTHING.

35:18.417 --> 35:20.552
- SO WHERE ARE WE
WITH FOREIGN MILITARY?

35:20.586 --> 35:22.388
- WELL, THE STATE DEPARTMENT
WAS ABLE TO GET ACCESS

35:22.421 --> 35:24.656
TO A DATABASE
OF INTERNATIONAL SHIP LOGS.

35:24.690 --> 35:27.393
OKAY, SO THREE FOREIGN VESSELS
MADE PORT STOPS

35:27.426 --> 35:28.594
THAT MATCH
ALL OF THE ATTACKS.

35:28.627 --> 35:31.163
- YEAH, A CANADIAN DESTROYER,
COLOMBIAN MARINE CRUISER,

35:31.197 --> 35:32.431
AND A BRAZILIAN FRIGATE.

35:32.464 --> 35:34.233
- GINA AND ARIEL
BOTH SAID

35:34.266 --> 35:35.667
THAT THE RAPIST
NEVER SPOKE.

35:35.701 --> 35:38.170
IT COULD BE BECAUSE HE HAD
AN IDENTIFIABLE ACCENT.

35:38.204 --> 35:39.738
- BUT YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT THE UNIFORM.

35:39.771 --> 35:42.274
LOOK AT THIS.

35:42.308 --> 35:45.444
CANADIAN NAVY
AND COLOMBIAN MARINES

35:45.477 --> 35:46.678
WEAR DIFFERENT COLORS
AND DIFFERENT TYPE SHIRTS,

35:46.712 --> 35:49.548
BUT CHECK THIS OUT.

35:49.581 --> 35:51.350
- BRAZILIAN NAVY--
THAT UNI

35:51.383 --> 35:52.684
LOOKS VERY SIMILAR
TO OURS.

35:52.718 --> 35:53.952
- YEAH, IT'S EASY

35:53.985 --> 35:56.455
FOR A WITNESS OR A VICTIM
TO CONFUSE.

35:56.488 --> 35:59.658
- OKAY, SO THE BRAZILIAN SHIP
THAT MATCHED--THE MARANHAO--

35:59.691 --> 36:02.661
IT'S LEAVING TOMORROW, BUT RIGHT
NOW IT'S DOCKED AT PIER 88.

36:02.694 --> 36:04.963
- SO WE'VE NARROWED IT DOWN
TO 3,000 SUSPECTS.

36:04.996 --> 36:06.798
- WE ALREADY KNOW
A FEW OF THEM.

36:06.832 --> 36:09.701
I MEAN, JAVIER, MARCO--
THEY WERE WITNESSES AT THE BAR.

36:09.735 --> 36:12.371
WE REINTERVIEWED THEM THE OTHER
DAY RIGHT BY THEIR SHIP.

36:12.404 --> 36:15.441
- JAVIER POINTED THE FINGER
AT OMAR EIGHT YEARS AGO.

36:15.474 --> 36:17.509
IF HE'S THE RAPIST,
HE HAD MOTIVE TO SET HIM UP.

36:17.543 --> 36:20.446
- ALL RIGHT, BEFORE WE START
AN INTERNATIONAL INCIDENT,

36:20.479 --> 36:23.582
LET'S GET PHOTOS OUT
TO THE VICTIMS.

36:29.388 --> 36:34.293
- OH, MY GOD.
THAT'S HIM.

36:34.326 --> 36:39.398
WHAT DID I DO?
WHAT DID I DO?

36:51.943 --> 36:53.712
- THAT'S THE MAN
WHO RAPED ME.

36:53.745 --> 36:54.980
I'M POSITIVE.

36:55.013 --> 36:56.915
WHERE IS HE?
DID YOU FIND HIM?

36:56.948 --> 37:01.920
- WE'RE WORKING ON IT,
GINA.

37:01.953 --> 37:06.292
- HE'S BEEN DOING THIS
FOR EIGHT YEARS?

37:06.325 --> 37:09.561
[crying] SO IF YOU HADN'T
PUT AWAY THE WRONG MAN,

37:09.595 --> 37:11.997
THIS NEVER WOULD HAVE
HAPPENED TO ME!

37:16.602 --> 37:17.569
- I'M SORRY, GINA.

37:17.603 --> 37:19.905
- [sobs]

37:22.408 --> 37:25.511
- THAT'S TWO FOR TWO.
- RIGHT, THANKS.

37:25.544 --> 37:27.846
ARIEL ALSO I.D.'D JAVIER.
- WE GOTTA PICK HIM UP.

37:27.879 --> 37:30.649
- WE MAY BE TOO LATE.
THAT WAS FIN.

37:30.682 --> 37:32.818
JAVIER'S BUDDY MARCO
IS STILL ONSHORE,

37:32.851 --> 37:34.686
BUT JAVIER'S ALREADY
BOARDED THE SHIP.

37:34.720 --> 37:36.655
- YEAH, BUT THEY'RE DOCKED
IN OUR JURISDICTION.

37:36.688 --> 37:37.989
WHAT'S TO STOP US
FROM JUST GOING ON BOARD

37:38.023 --> 37:39.525
AND ARRESTING HIM?

37:39.558 --> 37:41.627
- ONLY ABOUT A DOZEN
INTERNATIONAL TREATIES.

37:41.660 --> 37:42.728
I SPOKE TO HADEN.

37:42.761 --> 37:44.630
NO WAY
BRAZILIAN AUTHORITIES

37:44.663 --> 37:46.798
WILL TURN OVER A SAILOR
TO U.S. LAW ENFORCEMENT.

37:46.832 --> 37:48.400
- WELL, WHAT ABOUT STATE?

37:48.434 --> 37:49.668
- WELL, IT COULD TAKE
DAYS TO GO

37:49.701 --> 37:51.570
THROUGH THE PROPER
DIPLOMATIC CHANNELS.

37:51.603 --> 37:53.639
- WE DON'T HAVE DAYS.
THEY SAIL TOMORROW.

37:53.672 --> 37:54.473
- YEAH, BUT JAVIER
DOESN'T KNOW THAT

37:54.506 --> 37:55.441
WE'RE LOOKING
FOR HIM YET, RIGHT?

37:55.474 --> 37:57.376
I MEAN, IT CAN'T BE TOO HARD
TO GET A SAILOR

37:57.409 --> 38:00.078
TO GO ON SHORE LEAVE.

38:00.111 --> 38:02.814
[rock music]

38:02.848 --> 38:04.783
- CLASSY PLACE.

38:04.816 --> 38:06.385
- OWNER'S A RETIRED COP.

38:06.418 --> 38:07.553
DOING US A SOLID.

38:07.586 --> 38:12.891
THINK HE MISSES
THE ACTION.

38:12.924 --> 38:15.961
- JAVIER JUST LANDED.

38:21.767 --> 38:24.002
- MARCO.

38:24.035 --> 38:25.571
DIDN'T THINK, UH,
MY FRIEND COULD HANDLE

38:25.604 --> 38:27.706
ANOTHER NIGHT
OF PARTYING.

38:27.739 --> 38:29.808
NOT TOO MANY GIRLS.

38:29.841 --> 38:31.877
- AINDA E CEDO, CARO.

38:31.910 --> 38:33.812
- SO LAST NIGHT--
WHAT IS THIS?

38:33.845 --> 38:36.615
- YOUR GOING AWAY PARTY.

38:36.648 --> 38:39.985
- [grunting]

38:40.018 --> 38:43.822
- WELL, I GUESS YOU'RE
A LEFTY, HUH, JAVIER?

38:43.855 --> 38:47.493
- [panting]

38:49.895 --> 38:51.597
- THEREFORE, WE BELIEVE

38:51.630 --> 38:53.599
THE PEOPLE NO LONGER
MEET THE BURDEN OF PROOF,

38:53.632 --> 38:55.701
AND WE MOVE
TO VACATE THE JUDGMENT.

38:55.734 --> 38:57.736
- MR. HADEN?

38:57.769 --> 39:00.906
- THE D.A.'S OFFICE
HAS NO OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.

39:00.939 --> 39:04.776
WE FULLY SUPPORT
THIS REQUEST.

39:04.810 --> 39:06.912
- MR. PENA...

39:06.945 --> 39:10.048
GIVEN THE NEW EVIDENCE
PRESENTED HERE TODAY

39:10.081 --> 39:12.851
AND THE GRAVE MISCARRIAGE
OF JUSTICE,

39:12.884 --> 39:15.621
THIS COURT SINCERELY
APOLOGIZES

39:15.654 --> 39:17.723
AND WILL NOT ALLOW YOU
TO BE INCARCERATED

39:17.756 --> 39:19.791
FOR ONE MINUTE LONGER.

39:19.825 --> 39:22.628
PURSUANT TO THE NEW YORK CODE
OF CRIMINAL PROCEDURE,

39:22.661 --> 39:25.030
ARTICLE 440.10,
I HEREBY VACATE

39:25.063 --> 39:27.699
THE JUDGMENT AGAINST YOU.

39:27.733 --> 39:29.167
YOU'RE A FREE MAN, SIR.

39:29.200 --> 39:30.869
[pounds gavel]

39:37.676 --> 39:40.546
- [crying softly]

39:48.787 --> 39:50.088
[knock on door]

39:50.121 --> 39:52.057
- [sighs] SO I JUST GOT
OFF THE PHONE WITH THE LAB,

39:52.090 --> 39:53.959
AND THEY'VE CONFIRMED
THAT JAVIER'S DNA

39:53.992 --> 39:56.061
IS A MATCH TO ALL
FIVE CRIME SCENES.

39:56.094 --> 39:58.063
- AT THE END OF THE DAY,
YOU GOT YOUR GUY.

39:58.096 --> 39:59.865
- [sighs]

39:59.898 --> 40:02.801
- LIV, I WANT TO GIVE YOU
A HEADS-UP.

40:02.834 --> 40:07.138
THE D.A. HAS DECIDED TO START UP
A CONVICTION INTEGRITY UNIT

40:07.172 --> 40:08.707
ON PAST CASES.

40:08.740 --> 40:10.976
- OKAY.
- AND...

40:11.009 --> 40:12.844
THEY'RE GONNA START BY TAKING
A LOOK AT SEX CRIMES.

40:12.878 --> 40:15.747
- SO TWO DAYS AGO,
THE D.A. WAS CONTENT

40:15.781 --> 40:17.716
TO LET PENA ROT
IN PRISON,

40:17.749 --> 40:19.184
AND NOW HE WANTS
TO PLAY THE HERO?

40:19.217 --> 40:21.753
- WELCOME TO MY WORLD.

40:21.787 --> 40:22.788
BY THE WAY, UH,
DAVID HADEN

40:22.821 --> 40:26.792
WILL BE IN CHARGE
OF THE UNIT.

40:27.993 --> 40:29.895
- GOOD TO KNOW.

40:41.172 --> 40:42.140
- NIGHT.

40:42.173 --> 40:44.676
- YOU TOO.

40:44.710 --> 40:45.911
NICK.
- YEAH.

40:45.944 --> 40:49.948
- YOU'RE A GOOD PARTNER.

40:59.758 --> 41:03.795
SO...CHIEF HADEN.

41:05.997 --> 41:07.232
CONGRATULATIONS.

41:07.265 --> 41:09.801
- THANK YOU.

41:09.835 --> 41:12.738
IT'S A BIG UNDERTAKING.

41:12.771 --> 41:13.905
I ASKED BAYARD ELLIS
TO BE

41:13.939 --> 41:15.907
A MEMBER OF MY OUTSIDE
ADVISORY PANEL.

41:15.941 --> 41:18.844
- I'M NOT SO SURE
THAT HE'S A JOINER.

41:18.877 --> 41:20.278
- [chuckles]

41:20.311 --> 41:22.147
GUESS WE'LL SEE.

41:22.180 --> 41:25.250
- SO...
WHERE DOES THAT LEAVE US?

41:25.283 --> 41:27.953
- IN CONFLICT.

41:29.855 --> 41:32.691
I'M GONNA BE LOOKING INTO CASES
THAT YOU HANDLED.

41:32.724 --> 41:35.527
- AND WE NEVER DISCLOSED.

41:35.561 --> 41:38.897
- IT'S NOT TOO LATE.

41:38.930 --> 41:41.867
BUT THAT MEANS
I'D HAVE TO RESIGN.

41:41.900 --> 41:45.637
- WELL, THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
YOU CAN'T DO THAT.

41:45.671 --> 41:46.938
IT'S WHAT YOU LIVE FOR.

41:46.972 --> 41:49.174
- SAYS WHO?
- SAYS YOU.

41:49.207 --> 41:53.111
THE FIRST TIME YOU WALKED
INTO OUR SQUAD ROOM.

41:53.144 --> 41:57.182
- I'D BE ASSIGNED
TO YOUR CASES.

41:57.215 --> 42:00.051
[sighs]

42:06.692 --> 42:07.859
YOU KNOW, THAT--
THAT MEANS WE--

42:07.893 --> 42:11.697
- [quietly]
I KNOW.

42:11.730 --> 42:16.935
US...

42:16.968 --> 42:21.707
THIS...

42:21.740 --> 42:24.275
NEVER HAPPENED.
